dct_description_sm: Large city map plus Index Map of entire city. This section encompasses Chelsea and the tract of land that would become Chelsea Heights and includes a legend box designating types of buildings (brick, wood, stone), water mains, sewers and fire hydrants. This is the lower left quadrant of a large map that has been divided into 4 digital images.
